  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with diabetes who are counseled by a peer coach (another patient with diabetes) will
      have improved glycemic control compared with usual care patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Peer coaches have controlled diabetes, patient study subjects have poorly controlled
      diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
